CrashReporter
=============
An uncaught exceptions handler for Android capable of reporting via mail.

Example
-------

protected ReportingExceptionHandler mDamageReport = new ReportingExceptionHandler(this, new ReportingExceptionHandlerSettings( "receiver@domain", "App Name Exception Report"));
 
	public void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
		super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
 
      	// Set default exception handler and report old crash
 		mDamageReport.run();
 		Thread.setDefaultUncaughtExceptionHandler(mDamageReport);
		...





